      • onResponse

        public abstract void onResponse(int correlationId,
              RPCResponse response)
        This is the only method that must be extended. Other methods that are able to be extended are onStart and onError.
        Parameters:
        correlationId -
        response - This will be the response message received from the core side. It should be cast into a corresponding RPC Response type. ie, if setting this for a PutFile request, the message parameter should be cast to a PutFileResponse class.
